      <h4><b>Strawberry Ice Cream</b></h4>
      
      <div class="text-left">
<p class="title"><b>INGREDIENTS:</b></p>
   <p>
      <li>2 Cups strained yogurt</li>
      <li>1/2 Package (100 ml) food cream</li>
      <li>1,5 Cup frozen strawberries</li>
      <li>4 Tbsp honey</li>
  </p>
