      <p class="title"><b>PREPARATION:</b></p>
      <li><b>1.</b> Pass the strawberries through the blender.</li>
      <li><b>2.</b> Mix yogurt, honey and strawberries in a bowl.</li>
      <li><b>3.</b> Beat the cream and add to the mixture.</li>
      <li><b>4.</b> Put the mixture in the freezer and mix every hour.</li>
      <li><b>5.</b> Wait for at least 4 hours then serve.</li> 
